title: Toya Wright Baby...Please Say The Baby!
itunes:title: Toya Wright Baby...Please Say The Baby!
description:
THU 10/20 - Toya Wright stops by The Breakfast Club to talk about her new book, "In My Own Words", the tragic deaths of her brothers, how Lil' Wayne has supported her during tough times and why she might have another child with Weezy!
